# WHAT ARE FIFO TOPICS ON SNS ?
ANS-:In AWS SNS (Simple Notification Service), FIFO (First-In-First-Out) topics are a type of SNS topic that provides exactly-once message delivery and strict message ordering
# WHAT IS SNS MOBILE PUSH ?
ANS-:  SNS Mobile Push is a feature that enables you to send push notifications to mobile devices, such as smartphones and tablets, across various platforms
# ON WHICH DILIVERY METHOD DO WE USE AND CONFIGURE THE SUBSCRIPTION ?
ANS-: In AWS SNS (Simple Notification Service), when you create a subscription to an SNS topic, you can choose from different delivery protocols based on the type of endpoint you want to send notifications to
 
